java.io.Serializable, DmcNamedObjectIF
public class MenuImplementationConfigDMO
extends MvwDefinitionDMO
implements DmcNamedObjectIF, java.io.Serializable

The MenuImplementationConfig is used to define the various classes that will be used to implement an actual menu structure based the MVW menu definitions.

The class specified by useClass must be derived from org.dmd.mvw.client.mvwmenus.base.MvwMenuFactory and have a zero arg constructor.
